```cs
type IMyInterface = 
    abstract member DoIt: unit -> unit 

type MyImpl() = 
    interface IMyInterface with 
        member __.DoIt() = printfn "Did it!" 

MyImpl().DoIt() // Error: member 'DoIt' is not defined 

(MyImpl() :> IMyInterface).DoIt() 

// ... but 
let doit (doer: IMyInterface) = 
    doer.DoIt() 

doit (MyImpl()) 

```
